","data":"<pre class=sf-dump id=sf-dump-140871544 data-indent-pad=\"  \"><span class=sf-dump-note>array:4</span> [<samp data-depth=1 class=sf-dump-expanded>
  <span class=sf-dump-index>0</span> => <span class=sf-dump-note>array:11</span> [<samp data-depth=2 class=sf-dump-compact>
    \"<span class=sf-dump-key>id</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-num>5</span>
    \"<span class=sf-dump-key>title</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"198 characters\">Hisense 55 Class M7 Series Mini-LED 4K UHD Smart Google TV (55M7QG, 2026 Model) - MiniLED, Hi-QLED, HDR10+, Dolby Vision, Dolby Atmos, AI 4K Upscaler, Game Mode Plus, ALLM, Google Assistant Built-in</span>\"
    \"<span class=sf-dump-key>slug</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"58 characters\">hisense-55-class-m7-series-mini-led-4k-uhd-smart-google-tv</span>\"
    \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description</span>\" => \"\"\"
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\">&lt;p&gt;The M7 Series gives you a brighter, more colorful picture with MiniLED technology, so movies, sports, and games look more lifelike. AI 4K upscaling makes everything you watch look sharper, even older content, while AI Smooth Motion keeps fast action clear with less blur. Dolby Vision&amp;middot;Atmos delivers a big, theater-like experience with rich picture and powerful sound. Game Mode Plus helps reduce lag for smoother, more responsive gameplay. With Google TV&amp;trade;, all your favorite streaming apps and live TV are in one place, making it easy to find something great to watch fast.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\">&lt;ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MiniLED:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Delivers vibrant brightness and finely tuned contrast, revealing detail in both shadows and highlights. Blacks look deeper, colors appear brighter, and every scene stays vivid, even in the daylight.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dolby Vision Atmos:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Two technologies. One unforgettable experience. At the heart of every story, Dolby Vision and Dolby Atmos transform what you see and hear into something vivid and immersive.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI 4K Upscaler:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Bring your favorite content to life in 4K quality. Deep-learning models analyze textures and edges in lower resolution images, reconstruct missing details, sharpen textures, and reduce noise&amp;mdash;elevating your cherished classics and favorite streams to our modern standards.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Game Mode Plus:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Upgrade your gaming with Game Mode Plus. With VRR and ALLM, the 60Hz panel keeps input lag low and the action fluid, making the gameplay feel smooth and natural, so even casual sessions feel clean and responsive.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Smooth Motion:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Enjoy smoother motion across every scene. Combining intelligent blur reduction with real-time frame prediction, it intelligently eliminates blur, judder and stutter. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re watching fast-paced sports or playing games, every movement appears crisp and fluid.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Google TV:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Google TV brings together 700,000+ movies, shows, and more across 10,000+ apps, plus 800+ free live TV channels &amp;mdash; organized all in one place.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"2186 characters\">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
      \"\"\"
