      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>title</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"29 characters\">LG 75 4K UHD UA75 AI Smart TV</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>slug</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"29 characters\">lg-75-4k-uhd-ua75-ai-smart-tv</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description</span>\" => \"\"\"
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\">&lt;p&gt;Bring home 4K resolution in an impressive range of screen sizes with LG UHD TVs. Enjoy swift, easy browsing and tons of personalized recommendations including over 400 free LG channels.* Spend less time searching and more time streaming with LG webOS 25. Focus on the screen with a slim and simple-to-mount design for a stylish view no matter where you hang it. For gamers, you can quickly customize your gaming experience in one location with the LG Game Optimizer. And, with GeForce NOW &amp;amp; Xbox Cloud Gaming included, you can automatically stream and get in the game.** *Internet connection and subscriptions to streaming services are required; number of LG Channels subject to change. **Subscription and compatible gaming controller are required.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\">&lt;ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;4K Resolution: Bring your favorite content to life in 4K resolution&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Free LG Channels: Get instant access to over 400 free channels with LG Channels (Internet connection required)&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;AI Processor: A thrilling watching experience powered by the Alpha 7 AI Processor Gen8&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Smart TV Platform: LG&amp;#39;s Award-Winning Smart TV platform powered by webOS for easy access to streaming apps&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Personalized Recommendations: Enjoy swift, easy browsing and tons of personalized recommendations&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Stylish Design: Slim and simple-to-mount design for a stylish view no matter where you hang it&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Gaming Features: Quickly customize your gaming experience with LG Game Optimizer and stream games with GeForce NOW &amp;amp; Xbox Cloud Gaming&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1560 characters\">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
        \"\"\"
