    <span class=sf-dump-index>3</span> => <span class=sf-dump-note>array:11</span> [<samp data-depth=3 class=sf-dump-compact>
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>id</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-num>2</span>
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>title</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"94 characters\">Samsung 85&#8221; Class M70HB Series Mini LED 4K UHD Samsung Vision AI Companion Smart Tizen TV 2026</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>slug</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"93 characters\">samsung-85-class-m70hb-series-mini-led-4k-uhd-samsung-vision-ai-companion-smart-tizen-tv-2026</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description</span>\" => \"\"\"
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\">&lt;p&gt;Bright, detailed colors pair together with deep, cinematic contrast in your favorite smart apps and video games thanks to precise control with Mini LEDs, delivering a realistic picture no matter what you watch. Get thousands of subscription free channels, including 700+ premium channels with Samsung TV Plus. Rest assured your personal data is secured with Knox Security.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\">&lt;ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Mini LED Processor 4K Pure Spectrum Color-At the heart of your viewing experience, our powerful processor analyzes and enhances every scene, delivering 3X brighter highlights and 2X deeper blacks&amp;sup1; than standard 4K TVs, for lifelike detail and vibrant colors.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Pure Spectrum Color-This groundbreaking display technology combines an advanced color layer with Mini LED precision, enabling one billion stunning shades of color. Your content appears more vibrant and lifelike than ever before. From subtle skin tones to rich landscapes, every hue is vivid across the entire screen.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Mini LED HDR-Mini LED HDR takes your viewing experience to the next level by delivering exceptional brightness and contrast. It ensures that every scene is rich in detail, with colors that are more vibrant and lifelike. Compared to previous models, Mini LED HDR offers greater brightness and deeper blacks,&amp;sup2; creating a truly immersive experience.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Endless Free Content-Dive into endless entertainment with 2,700+ free streaming options, including 750+ subscription free channels on Samsung TV Plus-all with just an internet connection. Stay updated with live news, enjoy blockbuster movies or explore kids&amp;#39; shows and international hits. With thousands of on demand movies and fresh content added regularly, there&amp;rsquo;s always something new to watch. Free, convenient and packed with variety, it&amp;#39;s entertainment for every occasion.&amp;sup3;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Supreme Mini LED Dimming-Supreme Mini LED Dimming ensures that details are visible, whether it&amp;#39;s a dark shadow or a bright highlight, for a truly superb picture.&#8308;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Motion Xcelerator + DLG 120Hz-Perfect for gaming and sports, Motion Xcelerator + DLG 120Hz delivers fast, responsive performance.&#8309; Whether you&amp;rsquo;re navigating intense gameplay or keeping up with thrilling sports moments, enjoy clear visuals and smooth performance that keep you fully immersed in the action.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Color Booster-Every scene comes to life, from fiery reds and oranges to cool blues and greens. With Color Booster, all colors are enhanced, ensuring your favorite content is vivid and beautiful. Transform your viewing experience with rich hues and vibrancy.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Soccer Mode-Bring the excitement of the stadium into your living room with optimized settings for brightness, contrast, and motion. You&amp;rsquo;ll see every pass, shot, and goal in stunning detail with 40% better motion clarity and 30% more vibrant colors. Specifically designed for soccer, it enhances motion clarity to effectively track fast kicks and provides richer greens&#8310; for an authentic pitch look. As a result, crowd details and player movements appear sharper than ever.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Gaming Hub-Transform your TV into a gaming destination with Gaming Hub. Access your favorite titles from consoles, cloud services and gaming apps-all in one place, no console required. With personalized recommendations, discover hidden gems or revisit fan favorites. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re exploring new worlds, playing online with friends, or trying out a new cloud game, Gaming Hub makes it easy to jump right in with seamless access and hassle free navigation.&#8311;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Filmmaker Mode &amp;trade;-Experience content as it was meant to be seen with Filmmaker Mode.&#8312; This feature disables motion smoothing and sharpening, ensuring every film and show is displayed with the original colors, contrast and frame rate chosen by its creator. By removing distortions and enhancing color accuracy, Filmmaker Mode delivers a cinematic experience that stays true to the artistic vision behind the screen.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Compared to Samsung 2025 Q7F&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Compared to Samsung 2025 U8000F&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Samsung Account and internet connection required for network based smart services, including streaming apps and other smart features. Without Account log in, only external device connections (e.g., via HDMI) and terrestrial/over the air TV (only for TVs with tuners) available. Channels may vary by location and are subject to change. UI is subject to change without prior notice.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Supreme Mini LED Dimming is Software based (not full array hardware based) technology.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Available only on 55&amp;quot; class and larger screen sizes. DLG 120Hz increases refresh rate up to 120Hz, but will reduce image sharpness. Optimal for fast paced gaming; visual quality varies by title.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&#8310;40% clearer motion/30% richer greens vs. Q7F Sports Mode. Resulting picture may vary based on source content.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&#8311;Samsung Account required for network based smart services, including streaming apps and other smart features. Without Account log in, only external device connections (e.g., via HDMI) and terrestrial/over the air TV (only for TVs with tuners) available. Channels may vary by location and are subject to change. UI is subject to change without prior notice. High speed internet connection, additional gaming service subscriptions and compatible controller required.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&#8312;Filmmaker Mode logo is a trademark of UHD Alliance, Inc.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5487 characters\">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
        \"\"\"
