      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>id</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-num>4</span>
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>title</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"52 characters\">Philips 75 Class QLED 4K UHD (2160p) Google Smart TV</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>slug</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"52 characters\">philips-75-class-qled-4k-uhd-(2160p)-google-smart-tv</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description</span>\" => \"\"\"
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\">&lt;p&gt;The new Philips 75&amp;quot; Class 4K Ultra HD (2160p) QLED Google Smart TV brings together movies, shows, live TV and more from across your apps and organizes them just for you. Ask Google to find movies and shows, answer questions, control smart home devices, and more, with your voice. Experience a wider range of color, contrast and brightness output with quantum dot technology, bringing your movies even closer to reality. Binge-watch your favorite shows comfortably with advanced flicker-free and low blue light technology, reducing eye strain and fatigue. Find My Remote helps you locate your remote effortlessly. Simply press the locator button on your TV and hear your remote ring, even between cushions.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\">&lt;ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upgrade your viewing experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;4K with HDR10 for ultra-sharp images and vivid colors&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;4K QLED display allows for a greater color range and depth&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Modern stand and 3-sided borderless design&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;EyeCare technology for healthier and better viewing&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The entertainment you love, with help from Google&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Choose from 10,000+ apps for all your entertainment needs&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;800+ free live TV channels available&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Google Assistant makes it easy to search, discover, and more&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Multiple accounts &amp;mdash; For a personalized experience&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unlimited connected possibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Cast your mobile device to your TV with Google Cast&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Bluetooth&amp;reg; enabled with 802.11 AC for a wireless world&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;Never lose your remote again with Find My Remote&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1633 characters\">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
        \"\"\"
